code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeString(principal).     out.writeString(tokenString).     out.writeString(refreshToken).     out.writeTimeValue(expiresIn). }

@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     principal = in.readString().     tokenString = in.readString().     refreshToken = in.readString().     expiresIn = in.readTimeValue(). }
